title: Scarlet Taylor - Knits With Beads: Beautiful Gifts
description: It's knitting. It's beading. It's "Knit with Beads: Beautiful Gifts", the second book in the popular series. Like the first title, "Stunning Shawls and Wraps", this title introduces readers to the basics of knitting with beads and offers detailed instructions for such techniques as bead embroidery, beaded fringe, beaded knitting, slip-stitch beading, stranded beading, hook beading and bead knitting. In total, the book contains 18 inspired projects with fun gifts like: Cozy Neckwarmer and Puppy Love Sweater.
